A single enzyme fine-tunes red and yellow pigments in parrots‚Äô polychromatic plumage, according to a new Science study. 

The findings reveal new insights into the molecular mechanisms underlying the evolution and display of color variation in one of nature‚Äôs most colorful birds. https://t.co/UiARCoftJA
